      <title><![CDATA[滑屏插件]]></title>
      <url>/2017/08/03/%E6%BB%91%E5%B1%8F%E6%8F%92%E4%BB%B6/</url>
      <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="为什么写滑屏插件？"><a href="#为什么写滑屏插件？" class="headerlink" title="为什么写滑屏插件？"></a>为什么写滑屏插件？</h3><p>滑屏插件是我一直很想去写的一个jquery插件，之前一直没有机会，这一次刚好公司有这个需求，所以就写了一个。</p>
<p>说实话，写滑屏插件，真心不像在PC上面写图片轮播那么简单，它要考虑的东西会比较多。而且也会遇到一些安卓手机和苹果手机的兼容问题。花的时间还是有点久的。</p>
<h3 id="实现方式："><a href="#实现方式：" class="headerlink" title="实现方式："></a>实现方式：</h3><p>一开始在准备写这个插件的时候，首先考虑的是用什么样的方式来实现这样的效果。对于前端来说，实现动画无外乎js和css，参考了很多其他网站的做法，基本上都是通过css3的transition来实现。(PS:js来实现动画，主要是通过定时器或者requestAnimationFrame来实现，通过控制元素的top或left值来实现移动动画等)。<br><a id="more"></a></p>
<h3 id="遇到问题："><a href="#遇到问题：" class="headerlink" title="遇到问题："></a>遇到问题：</h3><ol>
<li>滑屏插件要考虑的因素比较多。比如，touch事件对于本身屏幕滑动的影响，滑屏方向的判断，滑屏临界点的判断，容易造成混乱。</li>
<li>当滑动到第一屏或者最后一屏的时候，再滑动的时候，就会浏览器就会返回上一页或者下一页。<h3 id="解决办法："><a href="#解决办法：" class="headerlink" title="解决办法："></a>解决办法：</h3></li>
<li>对于第一个问题，主要还是要代码逻辑清晰，api封装的时候要合理，这样就不容易混乱。</li>
<li>对于第二个问题，我解决的办法是，当滑动的时候(注意，只是在横屏滑动的时候，竖屏滑动的时候不用)，在body上绑定touchmove事件，阻止事件的默认行为，然后当出发touchEnd事件的时候，再解绑，这样就解决了这个问题。</li>
</ol>
<figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="comment">// 如果是竖屏滑动就不用阻止浏览器的默认行为</span></div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">this</span>.bindPreventDefault = <span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span> (<span class="params">e</span>) </span>&#123;</div><div class="line">	e.preventDefault();</div><div class="line">&#125;;</div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> (<span class="built_in">Math</span>.abs(<span class="keyword">this</span>.dataPos.offsetY) &lt; <span class="built_in">Math</span>.abs(<span class="keyword">this</span>.dataPos.offsetX)) &#123;</div><div class="line">    $(<span class="string">'body'</span>).on(<span class="string">'touchmove'</span> , <span class="keyword">this</span>.bindPreventDefault);</div><div class="line">&#125;</div><div class="line"><span class="comment">//解绑</span></div><div class="line">$(<span class="string">'body'</span>).off(<span class="string">'touchmove'</span> , <span class="keyword">this</span>.bindPreventDefault);</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="插件代码："><a href="#插件代码：" class="headerlink" title="插件代码："></a>插件代码：</h3><figure class="highlight kotlin"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div><div class="line">12</div><div class="line">13</div><div class="line">14</div><div class="line">15</div><div class="line">16</div><div class="line">17</div><div class="line">18</div><div class="line">19</div><div class="line">20</div><div class="line">21</div><div class="line">22</div><div class="line">23</div><div class="line">24</div><div class="line">25</div><div class="line">26</div><div class="line">27</div><div class="line">28</div><div class="line">29</div><div class="line">30</div><div class="line">31</div><div class="line">32</div><div class="line">33</div><div class="line">34</div><div class="line">35</div><div class="line">36</div><div class="line">37</div><div class="line">38</div><div class="line">39</div><div class="line">40</div><div class="line">41</div><div class="line">42</div><div class="line">43</div><div class="line">44</div><div class="line">45</div><div class="line">46</div><div class="line">47</div><div class="line">48</div><div class="line">49</div><div class="line">50</div><div class="line">51</div><div class="line">52</div><div class="line">53</div><div class="line">54</div><div class="line">55</div><div class="line">56</div><div class="line">57</div><div class="line">58</div><div class="line">59</div><div class="line">60</div><div class="line">61</div><div class="line">62</div><div class="line">63</div><div class="line">64</div><div class="line">65</div><div class="line">66</div><div class="line">67</div><div class="line">68</div><div class="line">69</div><div class="line">70</div><div class="line">71</div><div class="line">72</div><div class="line">73</div><div class="line">74</div><div class="line">75</div><div class="line">76</div><div class="line">77</div><div class="line">78</div><div class="line">79</div><div class="line">80</div><div class="line">81</div><div class="line">82</div><div class="line">83</div><div class="line">84</div><div class="line">85</div><div class="line">86</div><div class="line">87</div><div class="line">88</div><div class="line">89</div><div class="line">90</div><div class="line">91</div><div class="line">92</div><div class="line">93</div><div class="line">94</div><div class="line">95</div><div class="line">96</div><div class="line">97</div><div class="line">98</div><div class="line">99</div><div class="line">100</div><div class="line">101</div><div class="line">102</div><div class="line">103</div><div class="line">104</div><div class="line">105</div><div class="line">106</div><div class="line">107</div><div class="line">108</div><div class="line">109</div><div class="line">110</div><div class="line">111</div><div class="line">112</div><div class="line">113</div><div class="line">114</div><div class="line">115</div><div class="line">116</div><div class="line">117</div><div class="line">118</div><div class="line">119</div><div class="line">120</div><div class="line">121</div><div class="line">122</div><div class="line">123</div><div class="line">124</div><div class="line">125</div><div class="line">126</div><div class="line">127</div><div class="line">128</div><div class="line">129</div><div class="line">130</div><div class="line">131</div><div class="line">132</div><div class="line">133</div><div class="line">134</div><div class="line">135</div><div class="line">136</div><div class="line">137</div><div class="line">138</div><div class="line">139</div><div class="line">140</div><div class="line">141</div><div class="line">142</div><div class="line">143</div><div class="line">144</div><div class="line">145</div><div class="line">146</div><div class="line">147</div><div class="line">148</div><div class="line">149</div><div class="line">150</div><div class="line">151</div><div class="line">152</div><div class="line">153</div><div class="line">154</div><div class="line">155</div><div class="line">156</div><div class="line">157</div><div class="line">158</div><div class="line">159</div><div class="line">160</div><div class="line">161</div><div class="line">162</div><div class="line">163</div><div class="line">164</div><div class="line">165</div><div class="line">166</div><div class="line">167</div><div class="line">168</div><div class="line">169</div><div class="line">170</div><div class="line">171</div><div class="line">172</div><div class="line">173</div><div class="line">174</div><div class="line">175</div><div class="line">176</div><div class="line">177</div><div class="line">178</div><div class="line">179</div><div class="line">180</div><div class="line">181</div><div class="line">182</div><div class="line">183</div><div class="line">184</div><div class="line">185</div><div class="line">186</div><div class="line">187</div><div class="line">188</div><div class="line">189</div><div class="line">190</div><div class="line">191</div><div class="line">192</div><div class="line">193</div><div class="line">194</div><div class="line">195</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="comment">/**</span></div><div class="line"> * [switchPage description]  滑屏插件，该插件的动画效果是通过css3的transition来实现的。在安卓手机和苹果手机的表现都还不错。</div><div class="line"> * <span class="doctag">@param</span>  &#123;[object]&#125; options  该配置对象可以传入以下几个参数</div><div class="line"> * 1. beforeTouch : function , 在触屏滑动前的操作</div><div class="line"> * 2. touching : function , 在触屏滑动中的操作</div><div class="line"> * 3. afterTouch : function , 在触屏滑动结束时的操作</div><div class="line"> * 4. isClick : 布尔值 ， 是否可以使用点击来滑动切换内容，默认为false</div><div class="line"> * 5. isTouch : 布尔值 ， 是否可以使用touch事件来滑动切换内容，默认为true</div><div class="line"> * 6. clickNode : jQuery对象，配合isClick选项来使用，默认为null</div><div class="line"> */</div><div class="line">$.fn.switchPage = function (options) &#123;</div><div class="line">	<span class="keyword">if</span> (typeof options !== <span class="string">'object'</span> || !options) &#123;</div><div class="line">		optionis = &#123;&#125;;</div><div class="line">	&#125;;</div><div class="line">	<span class="keyword">var</span> defaults = &#123;</div><div class="line">		isClick : <span class="literal">false</span>,</div><div class="line">		isTouch : <span class="literal">true</span>,</div><div class="line">		clickNode : <span class="literal">null</span>,</div><div class="line">		afterTouch : function () &#123;&#125;,</div><div class="line">		touching : function () &#123;&#125;,</div><div class="line">		beforeTouch : function () &#123;&#125;</div><div class="line">	&#125;;</div><div class="line">	<span class="keyword">var</span> settings = $.extend(&#123;&#125; , defaults , options);</div><div class="line">	<span class="keyword">var</span> SwitchPage = function (node , options) &#123;</div><div class="line">		<span class="keyword">var</span> self = <span class="keyword">this</span>;</div><div class="line">		<span class="keyword">this</span>.settings = options;</div><div class="line">		<span class="keyword">this</span>.node = $(node);</div><div class="line">		<span class="keyword">this</span>.switchpageContent = <span class="keyword">this</span>.node.find(<span class="string">'.j-switchpage-content'</span>);</div><div class="line">		<span class="keyword">this</span>.switchpageWrap = <span class="keyword">this</span>.node.find(<span class="string">'.j-switchpage-wrap'</span>);</div><div class="line">		<span class="keyword">this</span>.clientWidth = $(window).innerWidth();</div><div class="line">		<span class="keyword">this</span>.clientHeight = $(window).innerHeight();</div><div class="line">		<span class="keyword">this</span>.dataPos = &#123;</div><div class="line">			distanceX : <span class="number">0</span></div><div class="line">		&#125;;</div><div class="line">		<span class="keyword">this</span>.count = <span class="number">0</span>;</div><div class="line">		<span class="keyword">this</span>.initPosition();</div><div class="line">		<span class="comment">//判断是否支持touch</span></div><div class="line">		<span class="keyword">if</span> (<span class="keyword">this</span>.settings.isTouch) &#123;</div><div class="line">			<span class="keyword">this</span>.node.on(<span class="string">'touchstart'</span> , function (e) &#123;</div><div class="line">				self.touchStart(e);</div><div class="line">			&#125;);</div><div class="line">			<span class="keyword">this</span>.node.on(<span class="string">'touchmove'</span> , function (e) &#123;</div><div class="line">				self.touchMove(e);</div><div class="line">			&#125;);</div><div class="line">			<span class="keyword">this</span>.node.on(<span class="string">'touchend'</span> , function (e) &#123;</div><div class="line">				self.touchEnd(e);</div><div class="line">			&#125;);</div><div class="line">			<span class="keyword">this</span>.bindPreventDefault = function (e) &#123;</div><div class="line">				e.preventDefault();</div><div class="line">			&#125;;</div><div class="line">		&#125;;</div><div class="line">		<span class="comment">//判断是否支持click</span></div><div class="line">		<span class="keyword">if</span> (<span class="keyword">this</span>.settings.isClick) &#123;</div><div class="line">			<span class="keyword">this</span>.settings.clickNode.each(function (index) &#123;</div><div class="line">				<span class="keyword">var</span> me = <span class="keyword">this</span>;</div><div class="line">				(function (index) &#123;</div><div class="line">					$(me).on(<span class="string">'click'</span> , function () &#123;</div><div class="line">						self.count = index;</div><div class="line">						self.transition();</div><div class="line">					&#125;)</div><div class="line">				&#125;)(index);</div><div class="line">			&#125;)</div><div class="line">		&#125;;</div><div class="line">	&#125;;</div><div class="line">	SwitchPage.prototype = &#123;</div><div class="line">		<span class="keyword">constructor</span> : SwitchPage,</div><div class="line">		initPosition : function () &#123;</div><div class="line">			<span class="keyword">var</span> self = <span class="keyword">this</span>;</div><div class="line">			<span class="keyword">var</span> w = <span class="keyword">this</span>.clientWidth;</div><div class="line">			<span class="keyword">var</span> h = <span class="keyword">this</span>.switchpageContent.outerHeight();</div><div class="line">			<span class="comment">//设置内容区的样式</span></div><div class="line">			<span class="keyword">this</span>.switchpageContent.css(&#123;</div><div class="line">				width : w,</div><div class="line">				height : h</div><div class="line">			&#125;);</div><div class="line">			<span class="comment">//设置内容区的父级的样式</span></div><div class="line">			<span class="keyword">this</span>.switchpageWrap.css(&#123;</div><div class="line">				height : h</div><div class="line">			&#125;);</div><div class="line">			<span class="comment">//设置最外层容器的样式</span></div><div class="line">			<span class="keyword">this</span>.node.css(&#123;</div><div class="line">				height : h</div><div class="line">			&#125;);</div><div class="line">			<span class="keyword">this</span>.switchpageContent.each(function (index) &#123;</div><div class="line">				self.dataPos[index] = index * w;</div><div class="line">				$(<span class="keyword">this</span>).css(&#123;</div><div class="line">					transform : <span class="string">'translate3d('</span>+(index * w)+<span class="string">'px , 0 , 0)'</span></div><div class="line">				&#125;)</div><div class="line">			&#125;);</div><div class="line">		&#125;,</div><div class="line">		<span class="comment">//触屏时</span></div><div class="line">		touchStart : function (e) &#123;</div><div class="line">			<span class="keyword">var</span> evt = e.originalEvent;</div><div class="line">			<span class="keyword">this</span>.dataPos.startX = evt.changedTouches[<span class="number">0</span>].pageX + <span class="keyword">this</span>.dataPos.distanceX;</div><div class="line">			<span class="keyword">this</span>.dataPos.startY = evt.changedTouches[<span class="number">0</span>].pageY;</div><div class="line">			<span class="keyword">if</span> (<span class="keyword">this</span>.settings.beforeTouch &amp;&amp; typeof <span class="keyword">this</span>.settings.beforeTouch === <span class="string">'function'</span>) &#123;</div><div class="line">				<span class="keyword">this</span>.settings.beforeTouch.call(<span class="keyword">this</span>);</div><div class="line">			&#125;</div><div class="line">		&#125;,</div><div class="line">		<span class="comment">//触屏滑动中</span></div><div class="line">		touchMove : function (e) &#123;</div><div class="line">			<span class="keyword">var</span> evt = e.originalEvent;</div><div class="line">			<span class="keyword">var</span> self = <span class="keyword">this</span>;</div><div class="line">			<span class="keyword">this</span>.dataPos.moveX = evt.changedTouches[<span class="number">0</span>].pageX + <span class="keyword">this</span>.dataPos.distanceX;</div><div class="line">			<span class="keyword">this</span>.dataPos.moveY = evt.changedTouches[<span class="number">0</span>].pageY;</div><div class="line">			<span class="keyword">this</span>.dataPos.offsetX = <span class="keyword">this</span>.dataPos.moveX - <span class="keyword">this</span>.dataPos.startX;</div><div class="line">			<span class="keyword">this</span>.dataPos.offsetY = <span class="keyword">this</span>.dataPos.moveY - <span class="keyword">this</span>.dataPos.startY;</div><div class="line">			<span class="comment">//左滑</span></div><div class="line">			<span class="comment">// 当横屏方向上滑动时，阻止浏览器的默认行为，竖屏滑动不阻止</span></div><div class="line">			<span class="keyword">if</span> (<span class="keyword">this</span>.dataPos.offsetX &lt; <span class="number">0</span> &amp;&amp; Math.abs(<span class="keyword">this</span>.dataPos.offsetX) &gt; Math.abs(<span class="keyword">this</span>.dataPos.offsetY)) &#123;</div><div class="line">				<span class="keyword">if</span> (<span class="keyword">this</span>.count &lt; <span class="keyword">this</span>.switchpageContent.length - <span class="number">1</span>) &#123;</div><div class="line">					<span class="keyword">this</span>.noTransition(<span class="keyword">this</span>.dataPos.offsetX - <span class="keyword">this</span>.clientWidth * <span class="keyword">this</span>.count);</div><div class="line">				&#125;;</div><div class="line">				e.preventDefault();</div><div class="line">			&#125;;</div><div class="line">			<span class="comment">//右滑</span></div><div class="line">			<span class="comment">// 当横屏方向上滑动时，阻止浏览器的默认行为，竖屏滑动不阻止</span></div><div class="line">			<span class="keyword">if</span> (<span class="keyword">this</span>.dataPos.offsetX &gt; <span class="number">0</span> &amp;&amp; Math.abs(<span class="keyword">this</span>.dataPos.offsetX) &gt; Math.abs(<span class="keyword">this</span>.dataPos.offsetY)) &#123;</div><div class="line">				<span class="keyword">if</span> (<span class="keyword">this</span>.count &gt; <span class="number">0</span>) &#123;</div><div class="line">					<span class="keyword">this</span>.noTransition(<span class="keyword">this</span>.dataPos.offsetX - <span class="keyword">this</span>.clientWidth * <span class="keyword">this</span>.count);</div><div class="line">				&#125;;</div><div class="line">				e.preventDefault();</div><div class="line">			&#125;;</div><div class="line">			<span class="keyword">if</span> (<span class="keyword">this</span>.settings.touching &amp;&amp; typeof <span class="keyword">this</span>.settings.touching === <span class="string">'function'</span>) &#123;</div><div class="line">				<span class="keyword">this</span>.settings.touching.call(<span class="keyword">this</span>);</div><div class="line">			&#125;;</div><div class="line">			<span class="comment">// 如果是竖屏滑动就不用阻止浏览器的默认行为</span></div><div class="line">			<span class="keyword">if</span> (Math.abs(<span class="keyword">this</span>.dataPos.offsetY) &lt; Math.abs(<span class="keyword">this</span>.dataPos.offsetX)) &#123;</div><div class="line">				$(<span class="string">'body'</span>).on(<span class="string">'touchmove'</span> , <span class="keyword">this</span>.bindPreventDefault);</div><div class="line">			&#125;</div><div class="line">		&#125;,</div><div class="line">		touchEnd : function (e) &#123;</div><div class="line">			<span class="keyword">var</span> evt = e.originalEvent;</div><div class="line">			<span class="keyword">this</span>.dataPos.endX = evt.changedTouches[<span class="number">0</span>].pageX + <span class="keyword">this</span>.dataPos.distanceX;</div><div class="line">			<span class="comment">//左滑</span></div><div class="line">			<span class="keyword">if</span> (<span class="keyword">this</span>.dataPos.endX != <span class="keyword">this</span>.dataPos.startX &amp;&amp; <span class="keyword">this</span>.dataPos.offsetX &lt; <span class="number">0</span> &amp;&amp; Math.abs(<span class="keyword">this</span>.dataPos.offsetX) &gt; Math.abs(<span class="keyword">this</span>.dataPos.offsetY)) &#123;</div><div class="line">				<span class="keyword">this</span>.transitionLeft();</div><div class="line">			&#125;;</div><div class="line">			<span class="comment">//右滑</span></div><div class="line">			<span class="keyword">if</span> (<span class="keyword">this</span>.dataPos.endX != <span class="keyword">this</span>.dataPos.startX &amp;&amp; <span class="keyword">this</span>.dataPos.offsetX &gt; <span class="number">0</span> &amp;&amp; Math.abs(<span class="keyword">this</span>.dataPos.offsetX) &gt; Math.abs(<span class="keyword">this</span>.dataPos.offsetY)) &#123;</div><div class="line">				<span class="keyword">this</span>.transitionRight();</div><div class="line">			&#125;;</div><div class="line">			$(<span class="string">'body'</span>).off(<span class="string">'touchmove'</span> , <span class="keyword">this</span>.bindPreventDefault);</div><div class="line">		&#125;,</div><div class="line">		transitionLeft : function () &#123;</div><div class="line">			<span class="keyword">var</span> self = <span class="keyword">this</span>;</div><div class="line">			<span class="keyword">if</span> (<span class="keyword">this</span>.count &lt; <span class="keyword">this</span>.switchpageContent.length - <span class="number">1</span>) &#123;</div><div class="line">				<span class="comment">// 当滑动距离超过屏幕的1/5时，才加1，加1就表示所有的容器位置都会向前移动</span></div><div class="line">				<span class="keyword">if</span> (Math.abs(<span class="keyword">this</span>.dataPos.offsetX) &gt;= <span class="keyword">this</span>.clientWidth / <span class="number">5</span>) &#123;</div><div class="line">					<span class="keyword">this</span>.count += <span class="number">1</span>;</div><div class="line">				&#125;;</div><div class="line">			&#125;;</div><div class="line">			<span class="keyword">this</span>.transition();</div><div class="line">		&#125;,</div><div class="line">		transitionRight : function () &#123;</div><div class="line">			<span class="keyword">var</span> self = <span class="keyword">this</span>;</div><div class="line">			<span class="keyword">if</span> (<span class="keyword">this</span>.count &gt; <span class="number">0</span>) &#123;</div><div class="line">				<span class="comment">// 当滑动距离超过屏幕的1/5时，才减1</span></div><div class="line">				<span class="keyword">if</span> (Math.abs(<span class="keyword">this</span>.dataPos.offsetX) &gt;= <span class="keyword">this</span>.clientWidth / <span class="number">5</span>) &#123;</div><div class="line">					<span class="keyword">this</span>.count -= <span class="number">1</span>;</div><div class="line">				&#125;</div><div class="line">			&#125;;</div><div class="line">			<span class="keyword">this</span>.transition();</div><div class="line">		&#125;,</div><div class="line">		noTransition : function (offset) &#123;</div><div class="line">			<span class="keyword">var</span> self = <span class="keyword">this</span>;</div><div class="line">			<span class="keyword">this</span>.switchpageContent.each(function (index) &#123;</div><div class="line">				<span class="keyword">var</span> distance = offset + <span class="keyword">this</span>.clientWidth * index;</div><div class="line">				$(<span class="keyword">this</span>).css(&#123;</div><div class="line">					transform : <span class="string">'translate3d('</span>+distance+<span class="string">'px , 0 , 0)'</span>,</div><div class="line">					transition : <span class="string">'transform 0s ease'</span></div><div class="line">				&#125;)</div><div class="line">			&#125;);</div><div class="line">		&#125;,</div><div class="line">		transition : function () &#123;</div><div class="line">			<span class="keyword">var</span> self = <span class="keyword">this</span>;</div><div class="line">			<span class="keyword">this</span>.switchpageContent.each(function (index) &#123;</div><div class="line">				<span class="keyword">var</span> distance = (index - self.count) * self.clientWidth;</div><div class="line">				$(<span class="keyword">this</span>).css(&#123;</div><div class="line">					transform : <span class="string">'translate3d('</span>+distance+<span class="string">'px , 0 , 0)'</span>,</div><div class="line">					transition : <span class="string">'transform 0.3s ease'</span></div><div class="line">				&#125;);</div><div class="line">				<span class="comment">//重置距离</span></div><div class="line">				self.dataPos.distanceX = self.clientWidth * self.count;</div><div class="line">			&#125;);</div><div class="line">			<span class="keyword">if</span> (<span class="keyword">this</span>.settings.afterTouch &amp;&amp; typeof <span class="keyword">this</span>.settings.afterTouch === <span class="string">'function'</span>) &#123;</div><div class="line">				<span class="keyword">this</span>.settings.afterTouch.call(<span class="keyword">this</span>);</div><div class="line">			&#125;;</div><div class="line">		&#125;</div><div class="line">	&#125;;</div><div class="line">	<span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="keyword">this</span>.each(function () &#123;</div><div class="line">		new SwitchPage(<span class="keyword">this</span> , settings);</div><div class="line">	&#125;)</div><div class="line">&#125;;</div><div class="line">$(<span class="string">'.j-indexpage-slide'</span>).switchPage();</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
]]></content>
      
        
